Application to repack video from mkv to mp4 and reencode audio to stereo aac.

INSTALL
Download the following files into suitable directories:

eac3to (http://www.videohelp.com/tools/eac3to)
mp4box (http://www.videohelp.com/tools/mp4box)
neroAacEnc (http://www.nero.com/eng/downloads-nerodigital-nero-aac-codec.php)

Modify the paths at the top of the repack.bat file to suit your locations.
Also make an empty "temp" folder where the script can place intermediate files and set that too.


USAGE
repack.bat filename.mkv